title: Feds, tech experts warned software on Clinton server was vulnerable to hack attacks
text:
0 Comment 
The private email server running in Hillary Clinton’s home basement when she was secretary of state was connected to the Internet in ways that made it more vulnerable to hackers, according to data and documents reviewed by The Associated Press. Full News here – FOX News Leave a Reply
